ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of JOCELYN WINTER FORMSMA of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum for Human Rights, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Wilton Littlechild, C.M., K.C., A.O.E., whose term will expire, effective February 28, 2023.
